Ing '''Bayabas''' (Biyabas o kaya Byabas), '''Guava''' keng [[English]](ibat keng [[Spanish amanu|Spanish]] '''Guayaba'''; '''Goiaba''' in [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]; '''Perakkya''' in [[Malayalam language|Malayalam]]) is metung yang genus ding mga 100 species ning [[tropical]] [[shrub]]s at malating [[pun]] tanaman ning myrtle family [[Myrtaceae]], katutubu king [[Caribbean]], [[Kalibudtang America]] at pangulung [[Mauling America]]. Deng [[bulung|bulung]] mililupa la misumangid, simply, elliptic anggang ovate, 5-15 cm kaba. Ding [[bulaklak]] maputi la, a atin limang petals at dakal a stamens. Ding ''Psidium'' species magagamit la bilang kakanan a tanaman dareng [[larva]]e da ring [[Lepidoptera]] species kayabe la ring ''[[Eupseudosoma|Eupseudosoma aberrans]]'', [[Eupseudosoma|Snowy Eupseudosoma]] at ''[[Hypercompe|Hypercompe icasia]]''.






































